            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Memmia Mar<lb break="no" n="3"/>cia vixit <lb n="4"/>annis XVIIII <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Mem</abbr><ex>mius</ex></expan> Mar<lb break="no" n="6"/>cus pater <lb n="7"/>eius et <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> Mar<lb break="no" n="8"/>tinus mari<lb break="no" n="9"/>tus eius et <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> Secun<lb break="no" n="11"/>dus <abbr>d</abbr> eius <lb n="12"/>coniugi <lb n="13"/><expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ientissimae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuerunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>In 3 Teile gebrochen. Inschriftfeld von Halbsäulen flankiert; oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes ein Kranz.</p>
            </div>
